statements.sql: select * from `users` where api_token = 'OoJETszcHcFVS3CR7yW2jxaaCenaoBXR2iZM8vIx8ZryIWONhHPPfwRspU1acc77ZyzXadwdo1alP1LtcVrJAFBwkiWqqXZxYfQP0wLrKjbGbI1Daivu24HVxZMvaGiALVm3GuyTeZa4hpZetAXQWU' AND status_user = 'aktif' limit 1

select cargo_pengiriman_details.nama_pengirim,
cargo_pengiriman_details.nama_penerima,
cargo_pengiriman_details.no_lmt,
SUM(cargo_pengiriman_barangs.biaya) as biaya,
SUM(cargo_pengiriman_barangs.jumlah_barang) as jumlah_barang,
keterangan,
jenis_barang_detail,
status_pembayarans.pesan,
DATE(cargo_pengiriman_details.created_at) as created from `cargo_pengiriman_details` left join `status_pembayarans` on `status_pembayarans`.`id_status_pembayaran` = `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`id_status_pembayaran` left join `cargo_pengiriman_barangs` on `cargo_pengiriman_barangs`.`no_lmt` = `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_lmt` where `no_manifest` = 2 group by `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_lmt`

select
SUM(cargo_pengiriman_barangs.jumlah_barang) as jumlah_barang,
SUM(cargo_pengiriman_barangs.biaya) as totalBiaya
from `cargo_pengiriman_details` left join `cargo_pengiriman_barangs` on `cargo_pengiriman_barangs`.`no_lmt` = `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_lmt` where `no_manifest` = 2 group by `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_manifest` limit 1

select trucks.no_pol,
trucks.sopir_utama as sopir_utama,
cargo_pengiriman_details.sopir,
cargo_pengiriman_details.no_manifest from `trucks` left join `cargo_pengiriman_details` on `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_pol` = `trucks`.`no_pol` where `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_manifest` = 2 group by `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_manifest` limit 1
